            "text1": "<p>With her background in design and marketing and with being the swiss army knife, she kickstarts ideas. <br/><br/>Superpowers: <br/>Multitasking at its best<br/><br/>Favorite thing to do within the company: <br/>Coming up with new product ideas</p>"
