            "title1": "Devy (Operations manager)",
            "text1": "<p>Devy has been the first employee and knows every single bit of the company. <br/>She knows the history, she was there when the first collar was born and keeps the whole company on track.<br/><br/>Superpowers:<br/>Numbers and excel sheets</p>"
          }
